OL,3,CMontgomeryshire & Glyndwr: How the
OL,4,Ctide turned for the typically Tory seat
OL,6,FMontgomeryshire is an area that has
OL,7,Ftraditionally opted for a Conservative
OL,8,Fmember of parliament but for the first
OL,9,Ftime, will now be represented by the
OL,10,FLabour party.
OL,12,FIt is an unprecedented win for the
OL,13,Fparty, now representing the area of
OL,14,Fnorthern Powys, but why the change
OL,15,Ffrom blue to red?
