OL,3,CMontgomeryshire & Glyndwr: How the
OL,4,Ctide turned for the typically Tory seat
OL,6,FRecent boundary changes saw the new
OL,7,Fconstituency of Montgomeryshire &
OL,8,FGlyndwr absorb a large part of Clwyd
OL,9,FSouth but before that, the old
OL,10,Fconstituency of Montgomeryshire was
OL,11,Fthe only seat in Wales that had never
OL,12,Fhad a Labour MP.
OL,14,FPresident of the Welsh Conservative
OL,15,FParty and former MP, Glyn Davies, said
OL,16,Fhe believed the new boundaries
OL,17,Fimpacted the result.
OL,19,F"I thought we were going to hold the
OL,20,Fseat," he said.
