OL,6,F"But if we were going to lose the
OL,7,Fseat, it seemed obvious to me it was
OL,8,Fgoing to be Labour.
OL,10,F"A lot of people thought it was going
OL,11,Fbe the Liberal Democrats, but it was
OL,12,Falways going to be Labour. Simply
OL,13,Fbecause of the way in which the
OL,14,Fboundaries changed, an awful lot of
OL,15,Fnorth Wales which is dominated by
OL,16,FLabour came into Montgomeryshire."
