OL,3,CMontgomeryshire & Glyndwr: How the
OL,4,Ctide turned for the typically Tory seat
OL,6,FConservative MP Craig Williams placed
OL,7,Fthird with 7,775 votes.
OL,9,FMr Williams recently admitted to
OL,10,Fcommitting a "huge error of judgment"
OL,11,Fwhen he was suspended from the party
OL,12,Fafter betting on the election date.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, local woman
OL,15,FJolie Williams said she believed the
OL,16,Fbetting scandal had turned many voters
OL,17,Faway from their typically Conservative
OL,18,Fvote.
